{"title":"你在高原之上——致孔繁森","authors":["朱悦华"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":7,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在高原之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——致孔繁森"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱悦华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"５０岁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪的一半"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的一生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用生命中最后的时光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世界上最高的高原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开你最洁白的情怀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老母、病妻、幼子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡不住你西去的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也支撑着你西去的脚步"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是无边的爱的包容"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温暖的小家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晾不开你鹏飞的翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阔远的高原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那神秘的雪国异彩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合着藏袍的命运之弦　拉开了你生命的悲壮序幕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从藏北大草原到喜马拉雅谷地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你将最深的情愫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路播撒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你走过的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的雪莲举出一个冬天的童话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清清的泉水映出阿里新美景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你怀揣着新阿里悄悄走了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那只风雨中的小羊羔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正用它轻快的蹄声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩响阿里的春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叩响沉默的高原"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你笑了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一抹深情将雪山照亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映红藏族老妈妈不干的泪痕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过穷乡闹市"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿过青丝白发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是时代共同的审美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就是喜马拉雅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就是雅鲁藏布"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一颗至诚的心灵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都在追随你不息的涛声"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}